RESET

OptionDescription
STILL MENU RESETReset all photo menu settings other than custom white balance and custom settings banks created using EDIT/SAVE CUSTOM SETTING to default values.
MOVIE MENU RESETReset all movie menu settings other than custom white balance and custom settings banks created using EDIT/SAVE CUSTOM SETTING to default values.
SET-UP RESETReset all setup menu settings other than DATE/TIME, AREA SETTING, TIME DIFFERENCE, and COPYRIGHT INFO to default values.
INITIALIZEReset all settings other than custom white balance to default values.

USER SETTING

# RESET

Reset shooting or setup menu options to default values.

# 1 Highlight the desired option and press MENU/OK.

| Option | Description |
| --- | --- |
| STILL MENU RESET | Reset all photo menu settings other than custom white balance and custom settings banks created using EDIT/SAVE CUSTOM SETTING to default values. |
| MOVIE MENU RESET | Reset all movie menu settings other than custom white balance and custom settings banks created using EDIT/SAVE CUSTOM SETTING to default values. |
| SET-UP RESET | Reset all setup menu settings other than DATE/TIME, AREA SETTING, TIME DIFFERENCE, and COPYRIGHT INFO to default values. |
| INITIALIZE | Reset all settings other than custom white balance to default values. |


2 A confirmation dialog will be displayed; highlight OK and
press MENU/OK.
